Does The Squatty Potty Actually Work?

In true fashion, our resident GP Dr Lucinda is back on the podcast to tackle this topic. Along with discussing the specifics of the squatty potty, Dr Lucinda also schools us on the best poo techniques.  

Find Dr Lucinda on Instagram here: https://www.instagram.com/todaywithdrlucia/?hl=en
